{"tid":2077840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港人，坐穩！] 呂秉權：人大應會在下周二通過國安法","createTime":"2020-06-24T14:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T15:40:38.000Z","uid":331566,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0e80a1bfa2c445abbd51fbc91ae71d5b363eca35","tid":2077840,"uid":331566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:47:49.000Z","msg":"呂秉權：「制度自信」是港區國安法的精髓<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/觀點/article/20200624/s00012/1592937018154/呂秉權-「制度自信」是港區國安法的精髓\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E%2Farticle%2F20200624%2Fs00012%2F1592937018154%2F%E5%91%82%E7%A7%89%E6%AC%8A-%E3%80%8C%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E8%87%AA%E4%BF%A1%E3%80%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E7%B2%BE%E9%AB%93&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=481c223b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E%2Farticle%2F20200624%2Fs00012%2F1592937018154%2F%E5%91%82%E7%A7%89%E6%AC%8A-%E3%80%8C%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E8%87%AA%E4%BF%A1%E3%80%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E7%B2%BE%E9%AB%93&h=587b9372\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/觀點/article/20200624/s00012/1592937018154/呂秉權-「制度自信」是港區國安法的精髓</a><br />\n/如無意外，全國人大常委會將在下周二通過《港區國安法》，趕及在7月1日香港回歸23周年、中共黨慶99周年（意味長長久久）前通過並實施。/<br />\n<br />\n陸陸續續有更多手足被上門拘捕、入獄，抗爭手法越縮越細，日日都睇新聞好嬲好嬲，但係大家記住呢個唔係結果，係過程！係我地光復香港嘅過程！國安法唔會撲滅香港人建國嘅心，只會加強。應承我，喺能力範圍內繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有坐緊政治監同坐緊冤獄嘅手足等緊我地救佢地出嚟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有 要幫所有烈士清算黑警<br />\n總有一日會煲底見！！！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">一息尚存，抗爭到底！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2ae7e200308613a770d11bd02b4f9453b04f673a","tid":2077840,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:48:38.000Z","msg":"快啦屌<img src